The Restaurant Serves Various Shakes, Hamburgers, Grilled And Fried Chicken Products, Fish, Salads, Fruit And Sandwiches. Mcdonald's Restaurants Are Owned And Operated By Independent Franchisees Of The Mcdonald's Corporation.
